<h1 id="head-b7295dfc58563eac21610bbbb32e29e376fbfd25">ToME 3 Spoilers</h1>
<span class="anchor" id="line-73"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-74"></span><p class="line874">Once the game is out, create spoiler pages using links in this format: <span class="anchor" id="line-75"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-76"></span><p class="line867"><tt class="backtick">&nbsp;*&nbsp;["/Spoiler&nbsp;Page"]</tt> <span class="anchor" id="line-77"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-78"></span><p class="line862">This way ToME 3 spoilers will be of the format SpoilerArchive/Something, while ToME 2 spoilers will be of the format Spoilers/Something. <span class="anchor" id="line-79"></span><span class="anchor" id="bottom"></span></div><p id="pageinfo" class="info" lang="en" dir="ltr">SpoilerArchive  (last edited 2007-12-08 20:18:30 by <span title="ShrikeDeCil @ c-71-197-236-94.hsd1.wa.comcast.net[71.197.236.94]"><a href="./ShrikeDeCil" title="ShrikeDeCil @ c-71-197-236-94.hsd1.wa.comcast.net[71.197.236.94]">ShrikeDeCil</a></span>)</p>

